Enum Term

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Term>
      • implementation.Term
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Term>

    public enum Term
extends java.lang.Enum<Term>
    Represents a term (semester, short-course, etc). Term can represent:
    • Fall
    • Spring
    • January short-course
    • Maymester course
    The Term enum can be extended at a later point to represent other similar terms.
